sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Analyste
    participant Frontend as React Dashboard
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant ML as ModelService
    participant XAI as SHAP Explainer
    participant LLM as FraudAgent
    participant DB as SQLite users.db

    rect rgb(240,248,255)
        Note over Analyste,DB: Phase 1 — Authentification
        Analyste ->> Frontend: Email + Password
        Frontend ->> API: POST /auth/login
        API ->> DB: Vérifier credentials
        DB -->> API: Utilisateur + role
        API -->> Frontend: JWT token + user
        Frontend ->> Frontend: Stocker token localStorage
    end

    rect rgb(255,250,240)
        Note over Analyste,DB: Phase 2 — Soumission Transaction
        Analyste ->> Frontend: Remplir formulaire transaction
        Frontend ->> API: POST /explain/shap
        API ->> ML: predict_and_shap(tx, model="xgboost")
        ML ->> ML: Preprocessor.transform()
        ML ->> ML: XGBoost.predict_proba()
        ML ->> ML: Calibration F0.5
        ML -->> API: fraud_probability + top_features
        API -->> Frontend: Score + SHAP (2-3s)
        Frontend ->> Frontend: Afficher jauge risque + barres SHAP
    end

    rect rgb(240,255,240)
        Note over Analyste,DB: Phase 3 — Explication LLM
        Frontend ->> API: POST /explain/llm
        API ->> LLM: explain(transaction, shap_features)
        LLM ->> LLM: Construction prompt
        alt Perplexity disponible
            LLM ->> LLM: Appel API Perplexity
        else Fallback Ollama
            LLM ->> LLM: Appel Ollama local
        else Fallback règles
            LLM ->> LLM: Template statique
        end
        LLM -->> API: Rapport NL (15-60s)
        API -->> Frontend: Explication complète
        Frontend ->> Frontend: Afficher synthèse IA
    end

    rect rgb(255,240,245)
        Note over Analyste,DB: Phase 4 — Sauvegarde & Annotation
        Frontend ->> API: POST /auth/transactions
        API ->> DB: INSERT transaction + résultats
        DB -->> API: OK
        API -->> Frontend: Transaction sauvegardée
        Analyste ->> Frontend: Annoter "Fraude Confirmée"
        Frontend ->> API: PUT /auth/transactions/{id}
        API ->> API: HITL save_feedback()
        API ->> DB: UPDATE annotation
        API ->> DB: INSERT human_feedback.parquet
    end

    rect rgb(245,245,255)
        Note over Analyste,DB: Phase 5 — Fine-tuning HITL (Superadmin)
        actor Superadmin
        Superadmin ->> Frontend: Panneau IA Learning
        Frontend ->> API: GET /hitl/status
        API -->> Frontend: 5 feedbacks en attente
        Superadmin ->> Frontend: Lancer fine-tuning
        Frontend ->> API: POST /hitl/retrain
        API ->> ML: XGBoost warm-start +50 arbres
        ML ->> ML: Sauvegarder modèle mis à jour
        ML -->> API: Modèle rechargé à chaud
        API -->> Frontend: Fine-tuning réussi
    end
